Gnomes are a diminutive race related to dwarves.  They like mining 
for precious gems, their favorite being the diamond.  They have large 
noses and large imaginations.  They do not have the reputation for 
being dour like dwarves do.  Perhaps this is because they do not live 
deep in the darkness of the earth like dwarves do, but rather in the 
sides of hills.  Many live in houses as well.  They are fond of strong 
drink, but have a strong sense of propriety as well, to head off 
excessive foolishness.  This does not hamper their proclivity toward 
practical jokes, however.
 
Gnomes cannot join the following guilds:  Necromancer.
